data.name: Label5.Text
data.value: One of the most useful features of [Program]. You can import other peoples settings and information, visit our web site as themed import files become available. You can also use the export and import wizards to backup and restore you own information. Please use the browse button to select your import file.

data.name: Label4.Text
data.value: Please select which items you would like to import from the items on the left.

data.name: Label2.Text
data.value: Please note, any missing items from the import file will be shown greyed out here.

data.name: Label6.Text
data.value: The import wizard has all the necessary information it needs to process the import file. Please press the Import button to start the process!
